At the vents, activity remained more or less the same as during the past days - vigorous liquid lava fountains from the NW flank vent as well as gas- and ash-rich lava fountains from the summit vents. A large surface lava flow from the flank vent remained active and had its front in the area of Todoque. (Photo: Tom Pfeiffer)" /></a>
